{"fixed_xml":"<ITEM>
  In denen Thurneysischen Buchl
  <BIBLIO>
    <DESCRIPTION>den allhier, seynd dato folgende zwey B
    </DESCRIPTION>
    <BOOK>
      <DESCRIPTION>acher zu haben, so in Nancy durch S
      </DESCRIPTION>
      <BIBL>
        <TITLE>Dictionnaire Universel- Francois & Latin, Vulgairement appell
        </TITLE>
        <EDITION>Dictionaire de Trevoux</EDITION>
        <NOTE>avec des Remarques d Erudition & de Critique</NOTE>
        <VOLUME>5. Tom.</VOLUME>
        <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
        <YEAR>1741</YEAR>
        <NOTE>davon die 3. ersten Tom. dato schon zu beziehen sind; das gantze Werck kostet samt der Fracht</NOTE>
        <PRIZE>fl. 24</PRIZE>
      </BIBL>
    </BOOK>
    <BOOK>
      <BIBL>
        <TITLE>Dictionaire Oeconomique, continant les moyens d'Augmenter son dien & de conserver sa sante</TITLE>
        <AUTHOR>Mister Noel Chomel</AUTHOR>
        <NOTE>Augmente dun Nouveau Supplement de deur Volumes, par</NOTE>
        <AUTHOR>F. Marset, Doct. en Medecines</AUTHOR>
        <NOTE>2vec fig.</NOTE>
        <FORMAT>2vec fig.</FORMAT>
        <VOLUME>4. Tom.</VOLUME>
        <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
        <YEAR>1741</YEAR>
        <NOTE>davon der erste Tomus dato bey ihnen zu beziehen ist; di</NOTE>
        <DESCRIPTION>gantze Werck kostet samt der Fracht</DESCRIPTION>
        <PRIZE>fl. 18</PRIZE>
      </BIBL>
    </BOOK>
  </BIBLIO>
  <BIBLIO>
    <DESCRIPTION>So dann sind bey ihnen auch genugsam annoch zu haben:</DESCRIPTION>
    <BOOK>
      <BIBL>
        <TITLE>Dictionaire Historique & Critique de Mr. Bayle</TITLE>
        <VOLUME>4. Tom.</VOLUME>
        <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
        <PLACE>Amsterd.</PLACE>
        <YEAR>1740</YEAR>
        <PRIZE>L. 27</PRIZE>
      </BIBL>
    </BOOK>
    <BOOK>
      <BIBL>
        <TITLE>Corpus Juris Civilis Romani, cum Notis Gotofrest</TITLE>
        <VOLUME>2. Tom.</VOLUME>
        <FORMAT>fol.</FORMAT>
        <YEAR>1740</YEAR>
        <PRICE>fl. 10. 48. xr.</PRICE>
      </BIBL>
    </BOOK>
    <BOOK>
      <BIBL>
        <TITLE>Dictionaire Royal, Francois-Allemand-Latin, par le R. P. Fr. Pomey</TITLE>
        <VOLUME>3. Voll.</VOLUME>
        <FORMAT>4</FORMAT>
        <YEAR>1741</YEAR>
        <PRIZE>fl. 5. 24. xr.</PRIZE>
      </BIBL>
    </BOOK>
  </BIBLIO>
</ITEM>","number_of_corrections":10,"explanation":"Added enclosing tags for better structure. Added <BIBLIO> to group the <BIBL> elements. Added <BOOK> to group the bibliographic entries. Corrected special characters. Added <DESCRIPTION> and <NOTE> tags to provide context to the text."}
